  <strong>Weekly front-end web development &amp; design tips, tricks, and tutorials</strong>. With a focus on HTML &amp; CSS, along with a splash of JS, some videos focus on properly understanding fundamental concepts, others explore little known or often misused CSS properties, and there are long series that explore taking everything and building out actual pages.</p>

<p>
  <a href="https://www.youtube.com/kevinpowell">My YouTube channel</a>
